<li><a href="http://www.zerotothree.org/site/DocServer/AttachmentandFosterCare.pdf?docID=2542" class="external text" title="http://www.zerotothree.org/site/DocServer/AttachmentandFosterCare.pdf?docID=2542" rel="nofollow">Zero to Three 2004 paper on use of attachment theory on foster care decisions</a></li>
</ul>
